title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H2 - Oct 22 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H2 - Oct 22 2022
description:
Every Republican should study and emulate Kari Lake. She responds to allegations she's an "election denier" by providing evidence of 150 Democrats denying election results. Husband's list of apologies goes viral. Devin Nunes, former chairman of the House Intelligence Committee and CEO of the Trump Media & Technology Group, on the latest developments on the Hunter Biden case and the Durham investigation. Animal Thunderdome: College wrestlers vs. grizzly bears.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
